### **SysBackground.enableDatadomeCaptchaSolver(autoOpen)**

**Description:**
The `SysBackground.enableDatadomeCaptchaSolver(autoOpen)` function enables the automatic solving of DataDome CAPTCHA challenges using the `SysContent.enableSafeDatadomeCaptchaSolver` method. The `autoOpen` parameter specifies whether the DataDome CAPTCHA anchor should automatically open or not.

**Parameters:**
- **autoOpen** (Boolean): If set to `true`, the DataDome CAPTCHA anchor will automatically open. If set to `false`, the anchor will not be opened automatically.

**Example:**

```javascript
SysBackground.enableDatadomeCaptchaSolver(true);  // Automatically open the DataDome CAPTCHA anchor and start solving.
```